ActCanada Shipping Act, 2001
SubjectNorthern Canada Vessel Traffic Services Zone Regulations
PrecisNORTHERN CANADA VESSEL TRAFFIC SERVICES ZONE REGULATIONS, in order to promote safe and efficient navigation and environmental protection. The Regulations apply to both Canadian vessels and foreign vessels that intend to enter and navigate within the VTS zone.
